/* fonts */
export const FontFamily = {
  ralewayMedium: "Raleway-Medium",
  ralewaySemiBold: "Raleway-SemiBold",
  ralewayRegular: "Raleway-Regular",
  ralewayBold: "Raleway-Bold",
  robotoRegular: "Roboto-Regular",
  ralewayExtraBold: "Raleway-ExtraBold",
  ralewayLight: "Raleway-Light",
  ralewayMediumItalic: "Raleway-MediumItalic",
};
/* font sizes */
export const FontSize = {
  size_smi: 13,
  size_5xs: 8,
  size_mini: 15,
  size_7xl: 26,
  size_sm: 14,
  size_xs: 12,
  size_3xs: 10,
  size_xl: 20,
  size_lg: 18,
  size_11xl: 30,
  size_6xl: 25,
  size_base: 16,
  size_4xs: 9,
  size_6xs: 7,
  size_2xs: 11,
};
/* Colors */
export const Color = {
  whitesmoke_100: "#f9f9f9",
  colorsBackgroundsLight: "#f5f5f5",
  whitesmoke_200: "#f3efef",
  whitesmoke_300: "#edecec",
  whitesmoke_400: "rgba(243, 243, 243, 0.4)",
  gray_100: "#fdfdfd",
  gray_200: "#959393",
  gray_300: "#8b8b8b",
  gray_400: "#8b8989",
  gray_500: "#7c7c7c",
  gray_600: "#2b2929",
  blackViolet900: "#0b0712",
  gray_700: "#090808",
  gray_800: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.58)",
  gray_900: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)",
  gray_1000: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6)",
  dimgray_100: "#666",
  blackViolet300: "#656070",
  dimgray_200: "#5c5c5c",
  redRed500: "#ff0066",
  palevioletred_100: "#fa6d8d",
  silver_100: "#b7b7b7",
  white: "#fff",
  black: "#000",
  lightgray: "rgba(215, 215, 215, 0.85)",
  darkgray_100: "#b0acac",
  darkgray_200: "#a6a6a6",
  indianred: "#924d4d",
  darkseagreen: "#96c486",
  darkslategray_100: "#414040",
  darkslategray_200: "rgba(65, 64, 64, 0.78)",
  lightpink_100: "#f498af",
  lightpink_200: "rgba(244, 152, 175, 0.55)",
  lightpink_300: "rgba(244, 152, 175, 0.58)",
  gainsboro_100: "#d9d9d9",
  gainsboro_200: "rgba(217, 217, 217, 0.58)",
  gainsboro_300: "rgba(217, 217, 217, 0.35)",
  gainsboro_400: "rgba(217, 217, 217, 0.4)",
};
/* Paddings */
export const Padding = {
  p_5xs: 8,
  p_11xs: 2,
  p_8xs: 5,
  p_base: 16,
  p_lgi: 19,
  p_31xl: 50,
  p_mini: 15,
  p_10xs: 3,
  p_3xs: 10,
  p_9xl: 28,
  p_6xs: 7,
  p_xl: 20,
};
/* border radiuses */
export const Border = {
  br_81xl: 100,
  br_7xs: 6,
  br_9xs: 4,
  br_xl: 20,
  br_5xs: 8,
  br_8xs: 5,
  br_16xl: 35,
  br_3xs: 10,
};
